cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and abstractive summarization. 
2. cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on summarization of spoken content. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses connectionist temporal classification (CTC) for sequence-to-sequence learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with a machine learning approach for natural language processing. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper deals with summarization of large corpora of spoken content.
